    <briefdescription>
<para>UDC endpoint buffer info. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure is mandatory for all UDC request. It contains the meta data about the request and is stored in user_data array of <ref refid="structnet__buf" kindref="compound">net_buf</ref> structure for each request. </para>
